Use the following:
For fonts:
Playfair Display (header)
Caveat (accent)
Montserrat (body)

For text colors and etc:

Nav:
  --nav-primary:   #306f91; --primary-color
  --nav-dark:      #1e4f6b; --dark 
  --nav-accent:    #4fb8e0; --accent

About us:
Replace with var(--name);
#333 → Dark gray (--secondary-light or --primary-dark:)
rgb(48, 111, 145) → (--primary-color)
#ffffff → White (--white)
#0a1f44 → Deep navy-blue  (--primary-dark:)

#0066cc → Bright blue -disregard
#2557c4 → Strong medium blue -disregard
#000000 → Black -disregard

Global:
/*For Website Colors*/
--white: #ffffff;
--dark: #1e4f6b; /*Darkest We can Go on Backgrounds*/
--accent: #4fb8e0; /*Like navbar background*/
--primary-color: #306f91; /*Logo Color*/
--primary-light: #afc3dc; /*Light Colored Backgrounds*/
--primary-dark: #11263b; /*Color for those Background is lighter*/
--secondary-light-dark: #356b86; /*Lighter Version(For Soft Look)*/
--secondary-light: #8a96b0; /*Light Gray*/
--secondary-dark: #234e63; /*Darker version of primary color*/
--soft-blue: #dceaf1; /*(For Soft Look)*/
--surface: #f5f9fb;   /*Off-White background*/
--surface-strong: #edf4f7; /*For it to pop on white BG*/
--surface-line: #d8e5ec; /*Border on white*/
--gold:       #F0B13D; /* For Buttons/ Accent-Text*/
--gold-dark:  #d9973a; /*For Buttons Hover*/
